WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.133 --> 00:00:03.266
Are you all right?

2
00:00:04.766 --> 00:00:06.166
What did he do to you?

3
00:00:06.166 --> 00:00:09.833
I'm fine, I just want to ask Mr. Lu for a favor

4
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:11.700
I didn't expect him to be angry.

5
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:14.300
What is your connection to the story?

6
00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:17.300
Because Chairperson Gu once funded me to study abroad

7
00:00:17.733 --> 00:00:19.033
I want to repay him.

8
00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:20.966
I know you go first

9
00:00:21.366 --> 00:00:22.766
Take him back first

10
00:00:27.333 --> 00:00:30.000
Uncle, you clearly know that he is my wife

11
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.300
What are you doing? I'm talking to him.

12
00:00:32.300 --> 00:00:34.233
Do you need to be together to talk about things?

13
00:00:34.266 --> 00:00:35.533
I know you don't believe it.

14
00:00:35.533 --> 00:00:38.433
But I'm here today on your mother's orders

15
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:39.200
Later yes

16
00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:41.066
He's not the kind of infidelity you usually play

17
00:00:41.066 --> 00:00:42.000
Heart woman

18
00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:45.900
And I warn you not to have any bad thoughts

19
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:47.400
I will tell my sister-in-law.

20
00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:50.066
And uncle, don't forget

21
00:00:50.066 --> 00:00:52.100
The road determines everything

22
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:53.500
In my hands

23
00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:54.666
You are the president

24
00:00:54.766 --> 00:00:56.300
But as far as I know

25
00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:56.666
Grandpa

26
00:00:56.666 --> 00:00:59.766
I haven't handed over the things of the people in power to you yet

27
00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:01.966
So uncle

28
00:01:02.533 --> 00:01:06.266
Are you going to fight with me? Hahahaha.

29
00:01:06.766 --> 00:01:09.400
The token is a wedding gift.

30
00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.800
Before you got married

31
00:01:11.933 --> 00:01:15.233
I'm afraid your position as president is still unstable

32
00:01:16.900 --> 00:01:20.033
Xiao Shuo, let's wait and see.

33
00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:24.400
Will make you proud of your own arrogance

34
00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.833
Arrogance pays the price

